'''Bobby Asghar''' is a Croatia-based English actor. He stars opposite Bertie Carvel as the Italian Apothecary in Cuba Pictures and BBC America's production of Jonathan Strange and Mr Norrell in 2014, directed by Toby Haynes and produced by Nick Hirshcorn.

In [[Season 5]] of Game of Thrones he will portray [[Catacomb Master #1]] opposite Emilia Clarke and Michiel Huisman, directed by Jeremy Podeswa.<ref>[http://www.imdb.com/name/nm6800489/]</ref>
